Once we pin down q,
we can, of course,

00:35:41.170 --> 00:35:43.845
go back and pin down l
and k, because l and k are

00:35:43.845 --> 00:35:45.960
a function of q.

00:35:45.960 --> 00:35:48.000
But this is where
it's one step harder.

00:35:48.000 --> 00:35:49.440
So this extra step
we have to take

00:35:49.440 --> 00:35:51.450
is we have to impose
the market condition

00:35:51.450 --> 00:35:53.720
to get to the little
q we want to produce.

00:35:53.720 --> 00:35:56.870
And in this case, that's 3.

00:35:56.870 --> 00:35:59.480
Questions about that?

00:35:59.480 --> 00:36:01.208
Yeah.

00:36:01.208 --> 00:36:03.000
AUDIENCE: So you know
how in the beginning,

00:36:03.000 --> 00:36:05.888
you said that in a perfectly
competitive market,

00:36:05.888 --> 00:36:07.430
the producers are
price [INAUDIBLE]??

