00:36:19.550 --> 00:36:20.060
JONATHAN GRUBER: Great.

00:36:20.060 --> 00:36:20.750
Great point.

00:36:20.750 --> 00:36:24.142
That's exactly-- we call that
a monopoly or an oligopoly,

00:36:24.142 --> 00:36:25.850
depending how you want
to think about it.

00:36:25.850 --> 00:36:28.250
They essentially
could monopolize.

00:36:28.250 --> 00:36:30.320
And we're assuming that
