00:47:06.950 --> 00:47:08.840
Negative 15.

00:47:08.840 --> 00:47:09.500
What's profits?

00:47:09.500 --> 00:47:11.580
Profits is revenues minus costs.

00:47:11.580 --> 00:47:12.550
Costs at zero--

00:47:20.630 --> 00:47:22.140
I'm sorry, you
